Package sensors

Interface Summary
DuelSensorTimer Interface that outlines the basic methods to be implemented for a sensor thread.
 

Class Summary
LightSensorTimer LightSensorTimer.java Implements a timer listener implementation of the light sensor.
SensorController Wrapper class to organize sensors.
UltrasonicTimer UltrasonicTimer.java Timer listener driven ultrasonic sensor thread
